(4, 'รีวิว “ เบตง 8 จุดเช็คอิน ห้ามพลาด ต้องแวะต้องถ่ายภาพ”', 0, 1, '<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"http://tourism.test/storage/reviews/June2021/2020-12_58985476b0fdf331.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"798\" height=\"532\" /></p>\r\n<h2><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center;\">รีวิว </strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center;\">&ldquo; เบตง 8 จุดเช็คอิน ห้ามพลาด ต้องแวะต้องถ่ายภาพ&rdquo; โดยล่องใต้ชายแดน</strong></h2>\r\n<p><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://tourism.test/storage/reviews/June2021/2020-12_a8eb3572116cb471.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"791\" height=\"527\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">1.ป้าย ok เบตง : บอกให้รู้ ว่ามาถึงเบตงแล้วน่ะ &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; fo